# Pre-push guard — personal marker list TEMPLATE.
#
# Copy this file to `.pii-markers.local` (which is gitignored and never
# published) and fill in YOUR personal strings — one regex alternative per
# line. '#' comments and blank lines are ignored. The guard always ALSO checks
# the generic API-key prefixes (sk-ant / sk-proj), so you don't list those.
#
#     cp scripts/pii-markers.example scripts/.pii-markers.local
#     # then edit .pii-markers.local with your own values
#
# Examples (REPLACE with your own — do NOT commit real values in this template):
# your-first-name
# your-last-name
# your absolute home directory path (e.g. slash-Users-slash-your-username on macOS)
# your-org-or-llc-slug
# your-private-project-folder
